#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Water, part 1
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:95 input:95
#: standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Water is the essence of life!"
msgstr "L'aigua és essencial per a la vida!"

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Water, part 2
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:97 input:97
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"Water is used by the gardener, by the forester, by all farms, and in the "
"bakery and the brewery. The fish farm and the sheep farm need to be supplied "
"with water, too."
msgstr ""
"Molts edificis i treballadors fan servir aigua: el guarda forestal, les "
"masoveries, les granges, la fleca i la cerveseria."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Log, part 1
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:108 input:108
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"Logs are an important basic building material. They are produced by felling "
"trees."
msgstr ""
"Els troncs són un material de construcció bàsic. Es produeixen talant arbres."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Log, part 2
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:110 input:110
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"European lumberjacks fell the trees; foresters take care of the supply of "
"trees. Logs are also used by the charcoal kiln, the shipyard and the sawmill."
msgstr ""
"Els llenyataires europeus talen arbres i els guardes forestals s'encarreguen "
"de replantar-ne. Els troncs també es fan servir als forns de carbó, a les "
"drassanes i les serradores."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Planks, part 1
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:121 input:121
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "Planks are an important building material."
msgstr "Els taulons són un important material de construcció."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Planks, part 2
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:123 input:123
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "They are produced out of logs by the sawmill."
msgstr "Es produeixen a partir de troncs a la serradora."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Planks, part 3
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:125 input:125
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "They are also used by the ferryyard and shipyard."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans ware: Blackwood
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:135 input:135
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"This fire-hardened wood is as hard as iron and it is used for several "
"buildings. It is produced out of logs in the wood hardener (basic sawmill)."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta fusta endurida amb foc és tan dura com el ferro i s'usa en diversos "
"edificis. Es produeix a partir de troncs a l'enduridor de fusta (una "
"serradora bàsica)."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Balsa
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:145 input:145
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"Balsa wood is an important trade ware. Balsa trees are cut by an experienced "
"woodcutter."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Ironwood
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:156 input:156
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"This very hard wood is as hard as iron. It is cut by a very experienced "
"woodcutter."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Scrap wood, part 1
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:167 input:167
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"Scrap wood is a waste material that arises from the demolition of buildings "
"or from sawmills."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Scrap wood, part 2
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:169 input:169
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "It can be processed into charcoal in charcoal kilns."
msgstr "Es pot processar en carbó vegetal en forns de carbó vegetal."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Reed, part 1
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:183 input:183
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "Reed is an important building material."
msgstr "El junc és un material de construcció important."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Reed, part 2
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:185 input:185
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "It is produced by the reed yard."
msgstr "Es produeix al camp de juncs."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Cotton, part 1
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:196 input:196
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "Cotton is a raw material used to make clothing."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Cotton, part 2
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:198 input:198
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "It is produced by normal farms."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Cloth
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:208 input:208
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "Cloth is needed to build several buildings. It is produced out of reed."
msgstr ""
"La tela és necessària per a la construcció d'alguns edificis. Es fabrica amb "
"juncs."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Rubber, part 1
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:218 input:218
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "Rubber is needed to make improved armor and boots."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Rubber, part 2
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:220 input:220
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "It is produced in tree nursery or in rubber farm."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Armor
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:230 input:230
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"Raw material for some sorts of armor. It is produced in the weaving mill out "
"of wool, cotton or reed."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Liana
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:240 input:240
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "Lianas grow on trees. Very durable ropes are made out of them."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Rope
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:251 input:251
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"This rope is made out of lianas. It is used for armor dresses and to "
"construct buildings and ships."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans ware: Honey
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:264 input:264
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"Honey is produced by bees belonging to a farm. It is used to feed animals."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans ware: Fruit
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:273 input:273
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"Fruit are berries gathered from berry bushes by a fruit collector. They are "
"used to brew fruit wine."
msgstr ""
"El fruit són petites baies recollides per un recol·lector de baies. S'usen "
"per fermentar vi de fruites."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Wool
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:282 input:282
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"The animal farm produces leather, which is used as a raw material for making "
"boots."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans ware: Fur
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:291 input:291
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"Fur is won from reindeer in a reindeer farm. It is woven into cloth or "
"turned into fur garments for soldiers."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Wool
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:300 input:300
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"Wool is the hair of sheep. Weaving mills use it to make armor. Animal farms "
"with level 4 or 5 can produce wool."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Atlantean ware: Spider Silk
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:309 input:309
#: standard
msgctxt "atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Spider silk is produced by spiders, which are bred by spider farms. It can "
"be processed into spidercloth or tabards in a weaving mill, or used to make "
"tools in the toolsmithy."
msgstr ""
"La seda d'aranya és produïda per aranyes, que són criades per granges "
"d'aranya. Es pot processar en tela d'aranya o tabards en una fàbrica de "
"teixits, o utilitzar-se per fer eines a la ferreria."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Atlantean ware: Spidercloth
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:318 input:318
#: standard
msgctxt "atlanteans_ware"
msgid ""
"Spidercloth is made out of spider silk in a weaving mill. It is used in the "
"shipyard. Also some higher developed buildings need spidercloth for their "
"construction."
msgstr ""
"La tela d'aranya està feta de seda d'aranya en una fàbrica de teixits. "
"S'utilitza a la drassana. També alguns edificis més desenvolupats necessiten "
"tela d'aranya per a la seva construcció."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Coal, part 1
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:331 input:331
#: standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Coal is mined in coal mines or produced out of logs by a charcoal kiln."
msgstr ""
"El carbó s'extrau de les mines i es produeix també amb troncs gràcies als "
"kilns de carbó vegetal."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Coal, part 2
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:333 input:333
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"The fires of the Europeans smelting works and smithies are usually fed with "
"coal."
msgstr ""
"Els focs dels forns de metalls i tallers dels europeus habitualment "
"s'alimenten amb carbó."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Granite, part 1
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:344 input:344
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "Granite is a basic building material."
msgstr "El granit és un material de construcció bàsic."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Granite, part 2
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:346 input:346
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "The Europeans produces granite blocks in quarries."
msgstr "Els europeus produeixen blocs de granit a les pedreres."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Granite, part 1
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:357 input:357
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "Grout is a basic building material."
msgstr "La lletada de calç és un material de construcció bàsic."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Granite, part 2
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:359 input:359
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"The Europeans produces grout in lime kiln or stonemasons house out of "
"granite and water."
msgstr ""
"Els europeus produeixen lletades de calç en forns de calç o als tallers de "
"pedra amb granit i aigua."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Clay, part 1
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:370 input:370
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "Clay is needed to make bricks."
msgstr "L'argila s'usa per fer maons."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Clay, part 2
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:372 input:372
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "The Europeans gets clay from gardeners house."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Brick, part 1
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:383 input:383
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "Brick is a basic building material."
msgstr "Els maons són un material de construcció bàsic."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Brick, part 2
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:385 input:385
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"The Europeans produces bricks in lime kiln or stonemasons house out of clay, "
"granite and water."
msgstr ""
"Els europeus produeixen maons en forns de calç o als tallers de pedra amb "
"argila, granit i aigua."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Marble
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:395 input:395
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"Marble is the beautiful stone which is cut out of the mountains or produced "
"in a quarry. Marble is used as a building material and gets chiseled into "
"marble columns in the stonemason’s house."
msgstr ""
"El marbre és una pedra magnífica que s'extreu de les muntanyes o es talla a "
"les pedreres. El marbre s'usa directament com a material de construcció o bé "
"després d'obtenir-ne columnes de marbre al taller de la pedra."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Marble Column
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:404 input:404
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"Marble columns represent the high culture of the Europeans, so they are "
"needed for nearly every advanced building. They are produced out of marble "
"at a stonemason’s house."
msgstr ""
"Les columnes de marbre són un element representatiu de la cultura europea. "
"Es fan servir en quasi tots els edificis avançats. Les columnes es tallen a "
"partir de blocs de marbre al taller de la pedra."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Iron Ore, part 1
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:417 input:417
#: standard
msgctxt "default_ware"
msgid "Ore is mined in ore mines."
msgstr "El mineral s'extrau de les mines."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Iron Ore, part 2
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:419 input:419
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid "It is smelted in a smelting works to retrieve all the metals."
msgstr "Es fon als forns de metalls per recuperar els metalls."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Gold, part 1
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:430 input:430
#: standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Gold is the most valuable of all metals, and it is smelted out of ore."
msgstr ""
"L'or és el metall més valuós. Es fon en forma de lingots a partir de mineral."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Gold, part 2
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:432 input:432
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"It is produced by the smelting works. Some valuable buildings need gold to "
"be built."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Copper Coin
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:443 input:443
#: standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid ""
"Copper coins are money made of copper or bronze (copper and tin). Its the "
"standard barter object."
msgstr ""
"Monedes fetes de coure o bronze (coure i estany) que serveixen per a "
"negociar."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Silver Coin
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:454 input:454
#: standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Silver coins are money made of silver. Its a valuable barter object."
msgstr ""
"Les monedes de plata són diners fets amb plata. És un objecte d'intercanvi "
"valuós."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Gold Coin
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:465 input:465
#: standard
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Gold coins are money made of gold. Its most valuable barter object."
msgstr ""
"Les monedes d'or són diners fets d'or. El seu objecte d'intercanvi més "
"valuós."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Quartz
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:475 input:475
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"These transparent quartz gems are used for trading. They are produced in a "
"mine."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans ware: Diamond
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:484 input:484
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_ware"
msgid ""
"These wonderful diamonds are used for trading. They are produced in a mine."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Carrier
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:501 input:501
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Used for recruiting all other workers."
msgstr "S'usa per reclutar altres treballadors."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Carrier
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:510 input:510
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Carries items along your roads with their hands."
msgstr "Porta béns pels camins amb les seves mans."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Carrier
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:519 input:519
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid ""
"Carries items along your roads with their hands. Only used for busy roads."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Carrier
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:528 input:528
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Carries items along your roads with baskets. Only used for busy roads."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Ox
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:537 input:537
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Carries items along your roads. They are reared in an animal farm."
msgstr ""
"Porta coses d'un lloc a l'altre pels camins. Es crien en granges d'animals."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Donkey
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:546 input:546
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid ""
"Donkeys help to carry items along busy roads. They are reared in an animal "
"farm."
msgstr ""
"Els ases ajuden a transportar béns en camins molt transitats. Es crien en "
"granges d'animals."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Horse
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:555 input:555
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid ""
"Horses help to carry items along busy roads. They are reared in an animal "
"farm."
msgstr ""
"Els cavalls ajuden a transportar béns en camins molt transitats. Es crien en "
"granges d'animals."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans worker: Tapir
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:564 input:564
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid ""
"Tapirs help to carry items along busy roads. They are reared in an animal "
"farm."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a Europeans worker: Reindeer
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:573 input:573
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid ""
"Reindeers help to carry items along busy roads. They are reared in an animal "
"farm."
msgstr ""
"Els rens ajuden a transportar béns en camins molt transitats. Es crien en "
"granges d'animals."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Worker
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:585
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:594 input:585
#: input:594 standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "General worker with no special ability."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Shipwright
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:603
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:612 input:603
#: input:612 standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Works at the shipyard and constructs new ships."
msgstr "Treballa a la drassana i construeix vaixells."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Ferry
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:621 input:621
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Ships wares across narrow rivers."
msgstr "Transporta béns a través de rius estrets."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Builder
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:630 input:630
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Works at construction sites to raise new buildings."
msgstr "Treballa construint nous edificis o desmantellant-los."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Lumberjack / Woodcutter
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:642
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:651 input:642
#: input:651 standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Fells trees."
msgstr "Tala arbres."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Ranger / Forester
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:660 input:660
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Plant trees."
msgstr "Planta arbres."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Gardener
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:669 input:669
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Making clay for lime kiln or stonemasons house and planting reed."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Gardener
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:678 input:678
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid ""
"Making clay for lime kiln or stonemasons house and planting reed, cotton and "
"rubber trees."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Europeans worker: Diker
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:687 input:687
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Constructs breakwaters to gain new land from the sea."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Geologist
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:699 input:699
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Discovers resources for mining."
msgstr "Descobreix recursos sota terra."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Stonecutter
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:708
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:717 input:708
#: input:717 standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Cuts blocks of granite and marble out of rocks in the vicinity."
msgstr "Talla blocs de granit i marbre de les roques properes."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Miner
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:726
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:735 input:726
#: input:735 standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Mines ore and minerals."
msgstr "Extrau minerals del terra."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Scout
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:747
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:757 input:747
#: input:757 standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid ""
"Scouts like Scotty the scout scouting unscouted areas in a scouty fashion."
msgstr ""
"Explora com Dora l'exploradora explorant inexplorades àrees de manera "
"experta."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Scout
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:767 input:767
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid ""
"Traders work in markets or in trading posts to exchange wares with other "
"tribes."
msgstr ""
"Els comerciants treballen a les botigues o als posts de mercaderies i "
"intercanvien béns amb altres tribus."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Recruit
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:776 input:776
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Eager to become a soldier and defend his tribe!"
msgstr "Amb ganes de convertir-se en soldat i defensar el clan!"

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an Europeans worker: Soldier
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:785 input:785
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_worker"
msgid "Defend and Conquer!"
msgstr "Defensa i conquereix!"

