msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"The forester’s house needs free space within the work area to plant the "
"trees."
msgstr ""
"La casa del guarda forestal necessita espais lliures dins l'àrea de treball "
"per plantar-hi arbres."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Rare Tree Plantation
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1489 input:1489
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Plants special trees, like balsa, liana, rubber and ironwood."
msgstr "Planta arbres especials, com balsa, lianes, cautxú i fusta de ferro."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Europeans production site: Rare Tree Plantation
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1491 input:1491
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid "Special trees are planted according to the economy requirements."
msgstr "Es planten arbres especials segons les necessitats de l'economia."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for an Europeans production site: Gardening Center
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1498 input:1498
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"Enhances the fertility of the landscape for trees. Also plants special "
"trees, like balsa, liana, rubber and ironwood."
msgstr ""
"Millora la fertilitat del paisatge per als arbres. També planta arbres "
"especials, com balsa, lianes, cautxú i fusta de ferro."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for an Europeans production site: Gardening Center
#: addons/europeans_tribe.wad/tribes/initialization/units.lua:1500 input:1500
#: standard
msgctxt "europeans_building"
msgid ""
"Only a Jungle Master has the necessary experience to coax more growth from "
"land."
msgstr ""
"Només un mestre de la selva té l'experiència necessària per aconseguir més "
"creixement de la terra."

